channel.title: What's wrong..?
channel.description:
I can't help it :\ I started trying to make servers about a month ago and failed at it so I want to post pics and see if anyone knows what I did wrong. This will get me back on track. Someone point out what I did wrong. I can already log onto my server though.
By the Way, the 3 digit numbers on starting ip address and the command prompt is my ip address on start>run>cmd>ipconfig. If that isn't the right ip, tell me what I am supposed to use for the portforward starting ip address. Someone said that they reset their router and before they did that their server worked. I've changed my router that is why my default gateway is not the default one like everyone elses
